## ğŸ›¡ï¸ Defense in Depth Model | Modelo de Defesa em Profundidade

### ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸ English Version
Defense in depth is a layered approach to vulnerability management that reduces risk by using multiple security controls to protect assets. This strategy improves an organization's **security posture**, which is its ability to manage the defense of its data and assets. The more valuable an asset is, the more advanced its protection should be.

