## âš™ï¸ Types of Security Controls | Tipos de Controles de SeguranÃ§a

Security controls are safeguards that reduce security risks.

| Control Type | Description (EN) | DescriÃ§Ã£o (PT) | Example |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Identity** | Authenticates users before access. | Autentica usuÃ¡rios antes do acesso. | Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA). |
| **Protective** | Shields against malicious attacks. | Protege contra ataques maliciosos. | Antivirus, WAF, IaC policies. |
| **Network** | Protects access through network paths. | Protege o acesso via rotas de rede. | Firewalls. |
| **Detective** | Identifies suspicious activity. | Identifica atividades suspeitas. | Intrusion Detection Systems (IDS). |
| **Responsive** | Uses automation to respond to events. | Usa automaÃ§Ã£o para responder a eventos. | Automatic email notifications of threats. |
| **Recovery** | Restores access and functionality. | Restaura o acesso e a funcionalidade. | System backups and restoration. |

